    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home an absolute masterpiece! This car is in breathtaking, mint condition, looking every bit as stunning as it did on the showroom floor. It has been cared for with the utmost pride, offering a flawless exterior and an interior that still feels brand new. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one for you!",
