    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a reliable daily driver in fair condition. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car remains dependable for commuting, please note that there are visible scratches and minor dents on the exterior, and the interior shows significant wear from regular use. It has been maintained adequately, though it may require some minor suspension work or a tune-up in the near future. This is an honest, high-mileage vehicle perfect for someone looking for affordable transportation without the showroom price tag.",
      "price": 20000.0,
